{"id":430230,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/02/邝飚_立场坚定斗志强/","date":"2016-02-27T02:15:52Z","modified":"2016-02-27T02:15:52Z","title":"邝飚：立场坚定斗志强","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】知名漫画家邝飚的微信公号“邝飚的灰色幽默”，在发布下文内容后不久即遭封号。<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%E4%BB%BB%E5%BF%97%E5%BC%BA%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%9A/\" target=\"_blank\">任志强“反党”</a>的话题在微信受到严格审查，更有不少公众号因发布支持任志强的内容而被销号。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/640-3.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430252\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430252\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/640-3.jpg\" alt=\"640\" width=\"500\" height=\"397\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/640-3.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/640-3-300x238.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color: #808080;\">《斗志强》局部</span></p>\n<p>这两天官媒正在“围剿”素有“任大炮”的任志强，缘由：2月19日上午，中共中央总书记、国家主席、中央军委主席习近平来到人民日报社、新华社和中央 电视台调研。当天下午，习近平在人民大会堂主持召开党的新闻舆论工作座谈会，强调党和政府主办的媒体是党和政府的宣传阵地，必须姓党，由此也就有了“党媒 姓党”的说法。而正是这个提法，引起了任志强的注意，通过微博表达了自己的不同观点……</p>\n<p>于是乎，类似文革式的大批斗场面出现了！</p>\n<p>我们先欣赏下旧图片：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7f48fd56-118a-4ac8-80df-583fd427331a.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430237\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430237\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7f48fd56-118a-4ac8-80df-583fd427331a.jpg\" alt=\"7f48fd56-118a-4ac8-80df-583fd427331a\" width=\"500\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7f48fd56-118a-4ac8-80df-583fd427331a.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7f48fd56-118a-4ac8-80df-583fd427331a-300x190.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/e3acf3d2-0819-422a-80ec-eb4c1fcee257.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430249\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430249\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/e3acf3d2-0819-422a-80ec-eb4c1fcee257.jpg\" alt=\"e3acf3d2-0819-422a-80ec-eb4c1fcee257\" width=\"475\" height=\"476\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/e3acf3d2-0819-422a-80ec-eb4c1fcee257.jpg 540w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/e3acf3d2-0819-422a-80ec-eb4c1fcee257-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/e3acf3d2-0819-422a-80ec-eb4c1fcee257-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/e3acf3d2-0819-422a-80ec-eb4c1fcee257-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/e3acf3d2-0819-422a-80ec-eb4c1fcee257-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/d0bc9135-ff7f-45c1-92f1-d1cab711ed91.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430248\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430248\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/d0bc9135-ff7f-45c1-92f1-d1cab711ed91.jpg\" alt=\"d0bc9135-ff7f-45c1-92f1-d1cab711ed91\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/d0bc9135-ff7f-45c1-92f1-d1cab711ed91.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/d0bc9135-ff7f-45c1-92f1-d1cab711ed91-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/b5df1234-bf08-4edd-8365-e1306d3cb183.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430245\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430245\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/b5df1234-bf08-4edd-8365-e1306d3cb183.jpg\" alt=\"b5df1234-bf08-4edd-8365-e1306d3cb183\" width=\"475\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/b5df1234-bf08-4edd-8365-e1306d3cb183.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/b5df1234-bf08-4edd-8365-e1306d3cb183-300x271.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2bee2e61-ac88-4426-8c24-991fa4dfc0a9.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430233\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430233\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2bee2e61-ac88-4426-8c24-991fa4dfc0a9.jpg\" alt=\"2bee2e61-ac88-4426-8c24-991fa4dfc0a9\" width=\"525\" height=\"371\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2bee2e61-ac88-4426-8c24-991fa4dfc0a9.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2bee2e61-ac88-4426-8c24-991fa4dfc0a9-300x212.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以上画面给了我创作这幅《斗志强》的灵感</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7b6ab98b-fa91-4d85-bd3f-eb9985153fe1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430236\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-430236\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7b6ab98b-fa91-4d85-bd3f-eb9985153fe1.jpg\" alt=\"7b6ab98b-fa91-4d85-bd3f-eb9985153fe1\" width=\"450\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7b6ab98b-fa91-4d85-bd3f-eb9985153fe1.jpg 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7b6ab98b-fa91-4d85-bd3f-eb9985153fe1-300x222.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color: #808080;\">公民任志强</span></p>\n<p>百度“任志强”，官媒的声音铺天盖地……</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f0ce3649-d842-4031-ab6e-fc32ff4ae2c1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430250\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430250\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f0ce3649-d842-4031-ab6e-fc32ff4ae2c1.jpg\" alt=\"f0ce3649-d842-4031-ab6e-fc32ff4ae2c1\" width=\"525\" height=\"471\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f0ce3649-d842-4031-ab6e-fc32ff4ae2c1.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f0ce3649-d842-4031-ab6e-fc32ff4ae2c1-300x269.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/4d7612cf-cc21-416e-ab2a-6f7b514a0e5e.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430235\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430235\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/4d7612cf-cc21-416e-ab2a-6f7b514a0e5e.jpg\" alt=\"4d7612cf-cc21-416e-ab2a-6f7b514a0e5e\" width=\"525\" height=\"524\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/4d7612cf-cc21-416e-ab2a-6f7b514a0e5e.jpg 567w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/4d7612cf-cc21-416e-ab2a-6f7b514a0e5e-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/4d7612cf-cc21-416e-ab2a-6f7b514a0e5e-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/4d7612cf-cc21-416e-ab2a-6f7b514a0e5e-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/4d7612cf-cc21-416e-ab2a-6f7b514a0e5e-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/756d85dc-2f01-4620-bf21-81f95a8aaa3f.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430241\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-430241\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/756d85dc-2f01-4620-bf21-81f95a8aaa3f.jpg\" alt=\"756d85dc-2f01-4620-bf21-81f95a8aaa3f\" width=\"440\" height=\"587\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/756d85dc-2f01-4620-bf21-81f95a8aaa3f.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/756d85dc-2f01-4620-bf21-81f95a8aaa3f-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>+++++++++++++++++++++++++++</p>\n<p>知名网友纷纷发微博：<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7ffd3db6-bae3-49dc-9b51-aed349a3934d.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430238\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430238\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7ffd3db6-bae3-49dc-9b51-aed349a3934d.jpg\" alt=\"7ffd3db6-bae3-49dc-9b51-aed349a3934d\" width=\"450\" height=\"610\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7ffd3db6-bae3-49dc-9b51-aed349a3934d.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/7ffd3db6-bae3-49dc-9b51-aed349a3934d-221x300.jpg 221w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++</p>\n<p>综合以上素材，我决定画之：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/8640ab49-b726-4441-9fd6-5bc27a8c304f.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430243\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430243\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/8640ab49-b726-4441-9fd6-5bc27a8c304f.jpg\" alt=\"8640ab49-b726-4441-9fd6-5bc27a8c304f\" width=\"475\" height=\"846\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/8640ab49-b726-4441-9fd6-5bc27a8c304f.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/8640ab49-b726-4441-9fd6-5bc27a8c304f-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/8640ab49-b726-4441-9fd6-5bc27a8c304f-575x1024.jpg 575w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><br />\n先用铅笔起稿，再用钢笔清稿。</p>\n<p>竖构图，挂铁丝牌子、戴大高帽，五花大绑、撅屁股等视觉元素定格下来。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/bb657a32-6d78-4127-83ea-bd3a48be290c.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430246\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430246\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/bb657a32-6d78-4127-83ea-bd3a48be290c.jpg\" alt=\"bb657a32-6d78-4127-83ea-bd3a48be290c\" width=\"475\" height=\"716\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/bb657a32-6d78-4127-83ea-bd3a48be290c.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/bb657a32-6d78-4127-83ea-bd3a48be290c-199x300.jpg 199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><br />\n用彩铅上色，并把关键词写出来，如实反映官媒的调性和措辞。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/640-3.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430252\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430252\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/640-3.jpg\" alt=\"640\" width=\"550\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/640-3.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/640-3-300x238.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n用高清相机拍好上传到电脑上做色温处理。《斗志强》完成！</p>\n<p>++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++</p>\n<p>这幅漫画贴到新媒体平台后，反响强烈。截图为证：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f8bb3f57-6694-4a3a-a89f-053884bbcd18.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430251\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430251\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f8bb3f57-6694-4a3a-a89f-053884bbcd18.jpg\" alt=\"f8bb3f57-6694-4a3a-a89f-053884bbcd18\" width=\"450\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f8bb3f57-6694-4a3a-a89f-053884bbcd18.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f8bb3f57-6694-4a3a-a89f-053884bbcd18-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/f8bb3f57-6694-4a3a-a89f-053884bbcd18-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/5975ff5f-5b7d-4f39-b883-883454035f98.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430242\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430242\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/5975ff5f-5b7d-4f39-b883-883454035f98.jpg\" alt=\"5975ff5f-5b7d-4f39-b883-883454035f98\" width=\"450\" height=\"657\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/5975ff5f-5b7d-4f39-b883-883454035f98.jpg 597w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/5975ff5f-5b7d-4f39-b883-883454035f98-205x300.jpg 205w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>在微信上……</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2dfe3b37-ea3c-40ce-b6e9-ca7757944f7d.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430234\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430234\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2dfe3b37-ea3c-40ce-b6e9-ca7757944f7d.jpg\" alt=\"2dfe3b37-ea3c-40ce-b6e9-ca7757944f7d\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2dfe3b37-ea3c-40ce-b6e9-ca7757944f7d.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2dfe3b37-ea3c-40ce-b6e9-ca7757944f7d-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/2dfe3b37-ea3c-40ce-b6e9-ca7757944f7d-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/acfdc748-7a9a-493a-9d27-1a6d68536a56.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430244\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430244\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/acfdc748-7a9a-493a-9d27-1a6d68536a56.jpg\" alt=\"acfdc748-7a9a-493a-9d27-1a6d68536a56\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/acfdc748-7a9a-493a-9d27-1a6d68536a56.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/acfdc748-7a9a-493a-9d27-1a6d68536a56-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/acfdc748-7a9a-493a-9d27-1a6d68536a56-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/c0cd57a4-af41-41d3-86c5-892df225d09b.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430247\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430247\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/c0cd57a4-af41-41d3-86c5-892df225d09b.jpg\" alt=\"c0cd57a4-af41-41d3-86c5-892df225d09b\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/c0cd57a4-af41-41d3-86c5-892df225d09b.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/c0cd57a4-af41-41d3-86c5-892df225d09b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/c0cd57a4-af41-41d3-86c5-892df225d09b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/98d4e74e-1b1c-4f30-9aaf-5800bd10dc87.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430239\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430239\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/98d4e74e-1b1c-4f30-9aaf-5800bd10dc87.jpg\" alt=\"98d4e74e-1b1c-4f30-9aaf-5800bd10dc87\" width=\"525\" height=\"690\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/98d4e74e-1b1c-4f30-9aaf-5800bd10dc87.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/98d4e74e-1b1c-4f30-9aaf-5800bd10dc87-228x300.jpg 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n<p>+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++</p>\n<p>此刻，这个漫画还在网络上发酵中……</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[30043,30383,24479,28993,30319,23589,29558,23674,9375,23203,8969,27151,8616,23882,25213]}